		text-align: center;
		font-size: 9pt;
		color: white;
		margin: 0px 0px 150px 0px;
	}

	.img1{
		position: absolute;
		top: 120%;
		left: 286px;
	}

	.img1 p{
		position: absolute;
		top: 70%;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 9pt;
